mitgutsch-fight.jpg.description: The man waving a white flag is located near the top-left of the image, sitting on a wooden panel in front of the window. He is wearing a blue suit and glasses.

whodoeswhat-city.jpg.description: The cello is located towards the left side of the image. It is brown and appears to be leaning against the wall of a green house with a brown roof. A person dressed in black is running towards it.

whodoeswhat-city2.jpg.description: The saxophone is in the bottom center of the image. A person wearing black is playing it, standing in the park area on the grass path, to the right of a small playground structure.

whodoeswhat-city3.jpg.description: The yellow electrical box is located near the bottom right corner of the image. It is on the side of a small orange building with a window, behind some tall concrete pipes. The box is mounted on the building wall.

river-adventure-house.jpg.description: The whale is a blue sculpture located near the top left of the image. It is placed on top of a yellow spiral slide in the swimming pool area, with grass and trees surrounding it.
The whale is a large decorative figure located on top of a yellow slide. It is blue and positioned near the top left area of the image.
